      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUNAWAY SAM (7) turned in a solid run fresh when finishing in the placings at this track in a Grade 5 (23.54). Will be much improved. Can find winning form. BLAZING BISCUIT (2) has been below best and missed the frame last couple, finishing 7th (24.01) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has won here at this journey. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. MISS ELPHABA (3) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, half a length from the winner Zipping Gressier (23.06) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to be in the finish again. VERGLAS (1) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
